<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>{تَحْوِيلًا <span class="c2">(٤٣)</span>} <span class="c4">[٤٣]</span> تام،<span class="c5"> واتفق علماء الرسم على كتابة:</span> <span class="c3">{سُنَّةَ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٣]</span> الثلاث بالتاء المجرورة.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{مِنْ قَبْلِهِمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٤]</span> حسن،<span class="c5"> ومثله:</span> <span class="c2">«قوة»</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{وَلَا فِي الْأَرْضِ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٤]</span> كاف.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>{قَدِيرًا <span class="c2">(٤٤)</span>} <span class="c4">[٤٤]</span> تام.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{مِنْ دَابَّةٍ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٥]</span> ليس بوقف؛ لتعلق ما بعده بما قبله استدراكًا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{إِلَى أَجَلٍ مُسَمًّى}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٥]</span> حسن.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{أَجَلُهُمْ}</span> <span class="c4">[٤٥]</span> ليس بوقف؛<span class="c5"> لأن قوله:</span> <span class="c2">«فإن الله»</span> جواب: <span class="c2">«إذا»</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
